# Image Tag & Registry Log
# Date: 2026-05-26

Image Build Information:

Base Image Tag (Local):
- fit4110/iot-ingestion:lab04

Recommended Tag Convention (v0.1.0-team-iot):
- Local: team-iot:v0.1.0-team-iot
- Or: fit4110/iot-ingestion:v0.1.0-team-iot

Command to Tag:
```bash
docker tag fit4110/iot-ingestion:lab04 team-iot:v0.1.0-team-iot
```

Optional: Push to Container Registry

If using GitHub Container Registry (ghcr.io):
```bash
docker tag fit4110/iot-ingestion:lab04 ghcr.io/<username>/team-iot:v0.1.0-team-iot
docker login ghcr.io
docker push ghcr.io/<username>/team-iot:v0.1.0-team-iot
```

If using Docker Hub:
```bash
docker tag fit4110/iot-ingestion:lab04 <dockerhub-username>/team-iot:v0.1.0-team-iot
docker login docker.io
docker push <dockerhub-username>/team-iot:v0.1.0-team-iot
```

Image Details:
- Base OS: python:3.11-slim
- Multi-stage build: Yes (builder + runtime)
- Size: Optimized (~300-400MB estimated)
- User: appuser (non-root)
- Ports: 8000 (uvicorn)
- Health Check: Configured with 30s interval
